{{ 'custom-cuehealth.css' | asset_url | stylesheet_tag }}

<div class="ch-page-hero">
  <div class="ch-page-hero__inner">
    <p class="ch-page-hero__eyebrow">CueHealth Policies</p>
    <h1 class="ch-page-hero__heading">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="ch-page-hero__sub">We respect your privacy and protect your data. Last updated: May 2026.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="ch-policy-wrapper page-width">
  <div class="ch-policy-content">

    <p>This Privacy Policy describes how <strong>VOXPLY LIFE SCIENCES LLP</strong> ("CueHealth", "we", "us", "our") collects, uses, and shares information about you when you use our website <strong>cuehealth.in</strong> and make purchases from us.</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <h3>1.1 Information You Provide</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Account information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, password</li>
      <li><strong>Order information:</strong> Billing address, shipping address, payment details (processed securely via Razorpay — we do not store card data)</li>
      <li><strong>Communications:</strong> Messages sent through our contact form or WhatsApp</li>
      <li><strong>Reviews:</strong> Product reviews and ratings you submit</li>
    </ul>
    <h3>1.2 Information Collected Automatically</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Device & browser data:</strong> IP address, browser type, operating system, referring URL</li>
      <li><strong>Usage data:</strong> Pages visited, time spent, clicks (via Google Analytics 4)</li>
      <li><strong>Cookies:</strong> See our Cookie Policy section below</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use your information to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Process and fulfill your orders</li>
      <li>Send order confirmations, shipping updates, and invoices</li>
      <li>Respond to customer support queries</li>
      <li>Send marketing communications (only if you opt in)</li>
      <li>Improve our website and product offerings</li>
      <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
      <li>Prevent fraud and protect security</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p>We share your information only with trusted third parties as necessary:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Shipping partners</strong> (ShipRocket and courier companies): Name, address, phone for delivery</li>
      <li><strong>Payment processors</strong> (Razorpay): Payment details for transaction processing</li>
      <li><strong>Analytics</strong> (Google Analytics): Anonymised usage data</li>
      <li><strong>Email marketing</strong> (Klaviyo/Mailchimp): Email if you subscribe to our newsletter</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We <strong>never sell</strong> your personal information to third parties.</p>

    <h2>4. Data Retention</h2>
    <p>We retain your personal data for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes described in this policy, typically:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Order records: 7 years (as required by Indian tax law)</li>
      <li>Marketing data: Until you unsubscribe</li>
      <li>Analytics data: 26 months</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. Cookies</h2>
    <p>We use cookies to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Keep items in your cart across sessions</li>
      <li>Remember your login</li>
      <li>Analyse traffic (Google Analytics)</li>
      <li>Show relevant ads (Meta Pixel)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>You can disable cookies in your browser settings. Note that disabling cookies may affect website functionality.</p>

    <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Access</strong> the personal data we hold about you</li>
      <li><strong>Correct</strong> inaccurate data</li>
      <li><strong>Delete</strong> your data (subject to legal obligations)</li>
      <li><strong>Opt out</strong> of marketing communications at any time</li>
    </ul>
    <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@cuehealth.in">hello@cuehealth.in</a>.</p>

    <h2>7. Security</h2>
    <p>We use industry-standard security measures including SSL encryption, secure payment processing via Razorpay, and restricted access to customer data. However, no method of internet transmission is 100% secure.</p>

    <h2>8. Third-Party Links</h2>
    <p>Our website may contain links to third-party sites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of those sites.</p>

    <h2>9. Children's Privacy</h2>
    <p>Our services are not directed to children under 18. We do not knowingly collect information from minors.</p>

    <h2>10. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Changes are effective immediately upon posting. Continued use of our website after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.</p>

    <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>For privacy-related queries, contact:</p>
    <p>
      <strong>VOXPLY LIFE SCIENCES LLP (CueHealth)</strong><br>
      Upper Ground Floor, 003, Kh No 485, Sector 73, Noida, UP – 201301<br>
      Email: <a href="mailto:hello@cuehealth.in">hello@cuehealth.in</a><br>
      WhatsApp: <a href="https://wa.me/917455918832">7455918832</a>
    </p>

  </div>
</div>

